fccb854307c","tid":1453833,"uid":232863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:48:32.000Z","msg":"〖白宮聯署狀況update〗Aug.13<br />\n<br />\n經過大家嘅努力，尋日有兩個聯署已達標。<br />\n而家按緩急輕重做個總表，方便大家拎去出post。<br />\n<br />\n建議方法：自己copy定，然後在不同地方留言時順便貼埋落去，提人 check email to confirm。多人做，咁人哋嘅page的留言區就會有大量聯署link。<br />\n<br />\n同去行街一樣，雖然沒有必勝法，但不敗方法就係「人多」。<br />\n<br />\n【未達標／極急／Aug 21 截】<br />\n請求國際制裁香港政府策動元朗恐怖襲擊！無差別襲擊平民百姓！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SxYeXZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SxYeXZ&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=ac509e28\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SxYeXZ</a><br />\n<br />\n【未達標】<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=63cca0b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d2c42a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n【已達標，但人數可以再多啲】<br />\n<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 (Sep.9 截)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=f09d7611\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求國際人道組織援助 (Aug.20 截)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GoVdnN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GoVdnN&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=7378a0a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GoVdnN</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織 (Sep.4 截)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=84ed5497\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a>"},{